The body of an 18-year-old girl was discovered in Athlone, Cape Town over the weekend. CAPE TOWN - Police have appealed for information to help an investigation into the death of a teenager in Athlone. The body of an 18-year-old girl was discovered over the weekend. Police spokesperson Constable Noloyiso Rwexana says an investigation is underway. "I can confirm that we are investigating a case of murder after an incident where police responded in Athlone. They found the body of an 18-year-old female." A relative, Dominique Hendricks, says she will remember her cousin's carefree spirit. "We don't know what happened but we need piece of mind on what led to her death, so that we can have answers and closure to give her a dignified burial."